  Updated ebuild to follow the policy about IUSE="".
  Updated Package HOMEPAGE and RDEPEND.

  29 Oct 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> junit-3.8.1.ebuild :
  Added dev-java/ant as a dependency. Fixes #9709.

